column5: Leaving from London either east to Lake Ontario for Salmon or west to Lake St. Clair for Muskie... any takers? I have all the gear and safety equipment needed.
NUTS! Gotta work tomorrow. Good luck wherever you end up
I wish I could, previous commitments for Saturday. Im north london. Maybe another time. Have a good and safe trip.  Matt
Just got home from work. If I'd known earlier I would have been interested. Good luck and don't forget a report.  Best wishes: Rick
Thanks for the offer, sadly I have to work one more shift before vacation   have a good time  Maureen

Hey Brian !!!! I have an empty seat for bass opener here in fmz17 as well !!!!! Lol .... Hope you do good today as I guess I'm heading out solo as well !!!!! Tight-lines.     Shawn. P.s I gotta get down your way and get on on lake at Clair with you one day !!!!! Cheers
Cats, smallies and a couple 'skis. We didn't get a good measurement on this one but its an easy 50...
Sorry team 2 but slowpoke took advantage of me typing the OFC 2013 logo on my phone and tossed back my easy 25"+ cat today so take it out on him
